name: CSULB Friend Finder
body:
### Welcome
This webpage will be the future home of the CSULB Friend Finder app. It will be developed by **Team 2** of the CSULB CECS 491 Tu/Th 7PM class of Spring 2015: **Nicholas Colburn**, **David Garcia**, **Kane Keller**, **Tan Tran**, **Gustavo Yepes**, and **Armando Zavala**.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
